4.description: Walk into the corner of C site near platform. Arrow 1: Aim halfway in this gap aligned with the edge of the top roof part. Arrow 2: Aim straight down, aligning with the edge of the bar.

4.name: Unbreakable A short knife
4.description: Line up the right side of the knife icon with the left tip of the leaf. Clears all of A short and close left site.

4.name: C site retake recon bolt
4.description: Line up with the middle of the window. Aim at the corner where the two walls meet

4.name: Haven C long plant double shock from C link
4.description: Get into the back corner of C link near B site. Arrow 1: Align the bottom left HUD with the corner of the dark wood. Arrow 2: Bring the crosshair down to the middle of the brick.

4.name: Haven B Front Site Recon Bolt
4.description: Line up the crosshair between the two edges of the window

4.name: Haven C site from attacker spawn
4.description: Reveals most of front and back site. Defenders can still hide behind middle box. Align the right diamond a few pixels to the right of the pink tree.

4.name: Haven A default post plant molly
4.description: Stand on the sandbags and aim the tip of the molly icon below the corner shown

4.name: Haven C default post plant molly
4.description: Line up the bottom left HUD line with the tip of the mountain as shown

4.name: Haven C long plant single shock dart from defender spawn
4.description: Get into the back corner of spawn near A site. Align the bottom edge of the 1st divider in the charge indicator with the leaf cluster.

4.name: Haven A fake arrow from C long
4.description: Line up the crosshair with the center of this leaf. Easier to get correct once you've done it.

4.name: Haven A site recon bolt from A link
4.description: Walk into the corner of A link. Place the top right corner of the charge bar into the shadow in the barrel.

4.name: Haven Mid doors recon bolt from C link
4.description: Go in the corner of C link with the potted plant. Align your crosshair with the square of the flag and move it to the left until it reaches the roof. Aiming too low will make the arrow land on the tree.

4.name: Haven A lobby recon bolt from A site
4.description: Get into the corner of the boxes at the back of A site. Place the tip of the shock dart icon to the vertex in the roof, as shown. Can spot enemies in A sewer. Must be precise.

4.name: Haven Mid recon bolt from C link
4.description: Go up against the wall at C link. Place the crosshair on the vertex of the tile as shown. Place the tip of the bottom right HUD line between the two parts of the roof as shown.

4.name: Haven C site recon bolt from C link
4.description: Get into the corner at the B site door towards C link. Place the upper right tip of the charge bar at the corner of the roof. Aiming lower will cause the arrow to fly past the wall.

4.name: Haven A Recon Bolt
4.description: Line up the second charge line slightly to the left of the light bulb. Lands on the edge of A heaven and reveals most of A site.

4.name: Haven garage recon bolt from mid window
4.description: First line up the two walls as shown. Then place the right side of the inner charge bar slightly to the right of the door.

4.name: Haven C long double shock dart from C back site
4.description: Walk into the corner of C site near platform. Arrow 1: Aim at about halfway on the marked part of the roof. Arrow 2: Aim down this extrusion, slightly to the left of the beam. No delay.

4.name: Haven A Long Single Shock Dart
4.description: Easy to see coming but can be used to push an op off angle

4.name: Haven garage recon bolt
4.description: Can also be lined up by moving into the corner of the barrier before the round starts. By using 1 bounce, it will not reveals close right corner. By using 2 bounces, it will not reveal close left.

4.name: Haven B site single shock dart from Mid
4.description: Go into the corner in mid across from the window. Aim top right from the faded brick on the wall.

4.name: Haven attacker side lobby recon bolt from B site
4.description: Get into the corner in the wall at B site. Hold forward and use mouse to guide the player model into a full stop. Place the crosshair onto the edge of the roofing, above and centered to the first window, as shown. This arrow can spot late pushers in A garden, Mid lobby, and C lobby.

4.name: Haven B site single shock dart from Mid
4.description: Go into the corner in mid across from the window. Aim above the center of the brick in the middle of the three darker bricks.

4.name: Haven A Recon Bolt
4.description: Reveals most of A site and short. Align the bottom left HUD line a few pixels above the leaf shown. Must be precise.

4.name: Haven C long entrance double shock dart from C back site
4.description: Walk into the corner of C site near platform. Arrow 1: Align the crosshair to the left of the bump and above the extrusion. Moving too far to the left will hit the edge of the roof. Arrow 2: Move the crosshair down until it reaches the bump in the roof. No delay.

4.name: Haven C site from C long
4.description: Jump on the corner and CROUCH. Place the top right dot of the charge bar to the left of the bottom left corner of the brown part of the window.

4.name: Haven C site from A lobby
4.description: Line up the bottom of the drone icon with the top of this pillar

4.name: Haven A garden recon bolt from B site
4.description: Walk into this corner of the crate. Aim at the bottom of the section dividing the two windows.

5.name: Icebox A default snakebite
5.description: Stand on the corner of the yellow line. Aim the crosshair above the right side of the opening in the wall. Bounces off the wall and covers default corner.

5.name: B default post plant snake bite
5.description: Line up with the middle of the yellow arrow on the door. Aim slightly to the right of the corner of the building and throw.

5.name: Icebox A default post plant molly
5.description: Line up the left side of the molly icon with the right corner of the generator

5.name: Icebox B mid site molly
5.description: Line up the crosshair slightly below the dark mark on the pillar

5.name: Icebox A default poison orb
5.description: Line line up the crosshair with the light on top, slightly to the right of the wall so it doesn't hit it and throw.

5.name: A default molly
5.description: Covers default plant and under rope

5.name: B top site poison cloud
5.description: Stand in the corner of the barrels, aim the diamond above the poison cloud icon below the corner in the image and throw.

5.name: Icebox B default post plant molly
5.description: Line up with the large white dot, aim the crosshair slightly above the middle of the top line in the image

5.name: Icebox B main recon bolt from Mid
5.description: Align the right drone circle slightly to the bottom left of the square on the building.

5.name: A gen/behind box molly
5.description: Line up the white dot above the molly hud with the white dot on the screen

5.name: B default molly
5.description: Stand on the right side of the light and line up the top right corner of the fuel bar with the corner of the crane

6.name: Split A front site post plant molly
6.description: There are a few ways to line this up, I use the bottom left HUD line

6.name: Split A clear close corners
6.description: Line up the crosshair where the corners of the building intersect. RUN and throw.

6.name: Split A Double Shock Dart
6.description: Can be used to stop early pushes on A site. Landing synced if done fast.

6.name: Split A ramp haunt
6.description: Line up the crosshair with the left light. JUMP and throw. Does not clear close left ramp.

7.name: Fracture B default post plant snake bite
7.description: Line up the tip of the snake bite icon with the edge of the roof

7.name: Fracture A post plant molly from sand
Fracture A satellite wallbang arrow
7.description: Reveals everything in front of dish and can be used to wallbang the other side

7.name: B tower molly
7.description: Line up the hud line above the molly icon with the bottom of the top right leaf. Must be precise

7.name: Fracture B back site post plant molly

8.name: Art/A main haunt
8.description: Stand in the corner with the box. Aim at the right edge of the roof and throw.

8.name: B site haunt
8.description: Stand in the corner in B long, aim at the bottom left part of the dip in the roof, jump and throw

8.name: Mid doors haunt
8.description: Stand against the left side of the buy phase barrier. Aim the the bottom of the line below the roof. Jump and throw

8.name: Post plant A site haunt
8.description: Stand in the middle of the box on the ground. Line up the top left part of the prowler icon with the tip of the lighter spike in the wall and throw.

8.name: A main control haunt
8.description: Stand against the buy phase barrier. Aim at the corner shown in the image and throw.

8.name: A site haunt
8.description: Take control of A main, stand in the corner on the left side of the artwork. Aim at the top of the wall above the line marked in the image. Run forward until the crosshair reaches the line below the top, jump and throw.

8.name: A site haunt
8.description: Stand on the left side of the box, line up the bottom left HUD line with the line on the wall as shown. Jump and throw.

8.name: A default post plant snake bite
8.description: Stand in the corner in A main. Line up the dot above the snake bite icon with the left corner of the pillar and throw.
